      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This car is ready for someone with a little DIY spirit! While it's seen better days and will definitely need some mechanical attention and TLC, it offers a great foundation for a fixer-upper. It's an affordable entry into vehicle ownership for anyone willing to put in the work!",
