    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is solid and reliable, with a smooth engine and transmission that perform as expected for its age. The exterior retains a nice finish, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
