    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this stunning vehicle in absolute mint condition! It looks and drives as if it just left the showroom, with a flawless exterior and a spotless interior that reflects meticulous care. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly maintained car that offers a like-new driving experience in every way!",
