    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine is currently non-running and will require extensive mechanical diagnostics and repairs. Externally, the body shows significant signs of age, including heavy rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and peeling clear coat. The interior has sustained considerable wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is and will need to be towed from its current location.",
      "price": 4500.0,
